    public class ExternalDebugger
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.bukkit.event.Listener
    There are two kinds of Debuggers - The 'Normal' one - The External one (this) Normal Debuggers often have a Dependency External Debuggers are own classes while Normal debuggers mostly print out the stuff that the Check currently does! You can find all External Debuggers in debug/debuggers The Normal Debuggers are Spread out over the hole Project You can get a List of ALL debuggers in the Debuggers class.
